fr.pcreations.labs.RESTDroid.core

Class Module

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.pcreations.labs.RESTDroid.core.Module

  • public abstract class Module
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to hold all your specifics needs without editing the core classes

    A module has to be register on WebService instance. It provides Processor, ParserFactory and DaoFactory that will be used during all process

    Version:
    0.5
    Author:
    Pierre Criulanscy
    See Also:
    Processor, ParserFactory, DaoFactory, WebService.registerModule(Module)
